object.content: http://www.alizspsychicsolutions.com.au/ - Call 1902 212 888- $2.97* per min GST incl./ higher rate for calls from payphones and mobile phones- and for credit cards, please visit the site for details.  Hello, I am Sharon; a Professional Psychic Counsellor, Clairvoyant and Reiki Master/Healer.I will tune into your energy and your Spirit Guardians and channel what you need to know at this time in your life, including;  Love, Relationships, Career, Desires and Dreams and anything you have put out into the universe!  Your loved ones whom have passed will come through too and your pets can talk to me as well!  I will also send healing energy to your soul through Reiki Distance Healing…I have been on Radio Talk Back discussing Spiritual Awareness, Healing and Meditation.  As a Meditation Teacher; I can assist  you in Meditation and Meditation Techniques…Your Energy Reading will be relaxed and comfortable, like confiding in a friend; you will feel that you are in a trusting and sacred space …With much love and light to you …Sharon
